message.content:
Rule Learning, Case Based. 

Rule Learning is present in the text as the system uses a set of rules to generate and evaluate design options. The manual also explains how to modify and create new rules to customize the system. 

Case Based is present in the text as the system uses a database of past design cases to generate new design options. The manual explains how to search and retrieve cases from the database and how to use them to generate new options.
